Issue :{" "} High Volume of patients seeking doctors for common ailments like cold, fever and viral infections and a scarcity of Healthcare professional compared to patient load leads to bottleneck and inefficiency.

Solution :{" "} This is a Medicine Recommendation System Developed to eliminate the bottleneck and improve the efficiency in treatments by automating the medicine prescription service for various common diseases which include Common Cold , Fever , Stomach Pain , Acne & so on. The System leverages the use of Knowledge Graphs , Large Language Models and Graph Data Science Algorithms to attain peak accuracy and robustness of the recommendations provided.

Chat with our Chatbot - Type in your symptoms to get the Medicine Recommendation and you are free to ask more about the medicine such as its price, TypeOfSell , Salts_Used , How_to_Use , How_it_Works , Side_effects & Alternate Medicines.
